## 📌 **About This Bot**

A **Telegram Bot** that generates **Pyrogram String Sessions** securely. Users provide API credentials, phone number, OTP, and 2FA (if enabled) to get their string session.

### ✨ **Features**
- 🔐 Generate Pyrogram string sessions
- 📱 OTP & 2FA support
- 🛡️ Rate limiting & session timeout
- 👥 Admin commands: `/stats`, `/users`, `/broadcast`
- 🗑️ Auto-delete messages after 10 mins
- 🚀 One-click deploy on Render

---

## 🔄 **How It Works**

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[User: /generate] --> B[Enter API_ID]
    B --> C[Enter API_HASH]
    C --> D[Enter Phone Number]
    D --> E[Enter OTP Code]
