🛠️ Installation

1. Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/telegram-string-bot.git
cd telegram-string-bot
```

2. Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

3. Create .env File

```bash
cp .env.example .env
```

4. Add Your Credentials in .env

```env
BOT_TOKEN=your_bot_token_from_BotFather
ADMIN_IDS=your_telegram_id
API_ID=6
API_HASH=your_api_hash_here
```

5. Run Bot

```bash
python main.py
```

