🛡️ Security Features

· ✅ No storage of API credentials, OTPs, or sessions
· ✅ Rate limiting (3 attempts per 5 minutes)
· ✅ Session timeout (auto-cancel after 5 minutes)
· ✅ Auto-delete sensitive messages after 10 minutes
· ✅ No sensitive data in logs
· ✅ Input validation for all user inputs

