🐛 Common Issues & Fixes

Bot Not Starting

```
❌ ERROR: BOT_TOKEN is required!
```

Fix: Set BOT_TOKEN in environment variables.

Admin Commands Not Working

```
⛔ You are not authorized!
```

Fix: Add your Telegram ID to ADMIN_IDS.

Rate Limit Exceeded

```
⚠️ Rate Limit Exceeded
```

Fix: Wait 5 minutes or increase RATE_LIMIT.

