📝 How to Get Credentials

1️⃣ Bot Token (@BotFather)

https://img.shields.io/badge/Telegram-@BotFather-2CA5E0?style=for-the-badge&logo=telegram&logoColor=white

1. Message @BotFather on Telegram
2. Send /newbot
3. Give name & username
4. Copy the token

2️⃣ Telegram ID (@userinfobot)

https://img.shields.io/badge/Telegram-@userinfobot-2CA5E0?style=for-the-badge&logo=telegram&logoColor=white

1. Message @userinfobot
2. Send /start
3. Copy your ID

3️⃣ API ID & Hash (my.telegram.org)

https://img.shields.io/badge/Telegram-API_Development-2CA5E0?style=for-the-badge&logo=telegram&logoColor=white

1. Visit my.telegram.org
2. Login with phone number
3. Go to "API Development Tools"
4. Create application
5. Copy API_ID & API_HASH

